com.guidewire.util.webservices
Interface SOAPAuthenticatedProxy

public interface SOAPAuthenticatedProxy

Internal interface implemented by SOAP proxy returned from APILocator.getAuthenticatedProxy(Class, String, String, String). The proxy can be cast to this interface to invoke its methods.

Method Summary
 boolean isConversational()
          Return true if this authenticated proxy is conversational (maintains state in the form of a session), false otherwise.
 int keyHash()
          Return the hash for the key associated with this authenticated proxy.
 void logout()
          Logout from the remote server with which this proxy is associated.
 

Method Detail

logout

void logout()
Logout from the remote server with which this proxy is associated. Calling logout will also remove this proxy from the pool of proxies managed by APILocator.
